    <edge source="CONTENT_ID" target="CONTENT">
      <data key="d4">36.0</data>
      <data key="d5">The CONTENT_ID entity serves as a unique identifier for each CONTENT item, utilized to track and analyze content information. This identifier plays a crucial role in distinguishing between different content items, enabling efficient data analysis and management of the CONTENT entity. By assigning a unique identifier to each content item, the CONTENT_ID facilitates the organization and examination of content information, providing valuable insights into the CONTENT entity's characteristics and behavior. The CONTENT entity, in turn, encompasses various content items, each associated with a distinct CONTENT_ID, thereby ensuring that each item can be accurately identified, tracked, and analyzed within the context of the CONTENT entity.</data>
      <data key="d6">d4c32cb337d90fe6c32a1507c69b61b3,dcf10bbfcd07ccf54a18b52e04a4d891</data>
    </edge>
